  <official_title>Comparison of Atrophogenic Effect of Hydrocortison 1% Cream and Pimecrolimus 1% Cream Assessed by Optical Coherence Tomography (OCT) and 20-MHz Ultrasound of Uninvolved Skin in Patients With Atopic Dermatitis</official_title>
